let-points/</link><description>&lt;img src="https://fortune.com/img-assets/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/GettyImages-2246892016-e1771610565606.jpg?w=1440&amp;amp;q=75" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 11:38:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://fortune.com/2026/02/20/how-does-elon-musk-hire-dojo3-chip-team-no-resumes-3-bullet-points/</guid></item><item><title>独家：Anthropic 推出人工智能工具，可以自行寻找软件错误，包括人类错过的最危险的错误</title><link>https://fortune.com/2026/02/20/exclusive-anthropic-rolls-out-ai-tool-that-can-hunt-software-bugs-on-its-own-including-the-most-dangerous-ones-humans-miss/</link><description>&lt;img src="https://fortune.com/img-assets/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/GettyImages-2259623291-e1771594509744.jpg?w=1440&amp;amp;q=75" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 11:23:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://fortune.com/2026/02/20/exclusive-anthropic-rolls-out-ai-tool-that-can-hunt-software-bugs-on-its-own-including-the-most-dangerous-ones-humans-miss/</guid></item><item><title>马克·扎克伯格的随行人员因佩戴 Meta AI 眼镜进入无录音法庭而受到蔑视威胁</title><link>https://fortune.com/2026/02/20/mark-zuckerbergs-contempt-of-court-meta-glasses-courtroom-trial-social-media-addiction/</link><description>&lt;img src="https://fortune.com/img-assets/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/GettyImages-2261799662-e1771608010320.jpg?w=1440&amp;amp;q=75" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 11:08:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://fortune.com/2026/02/20/mark-zuckerbergs-contempt-of-court-meta-glasses-courtroom-trial-social-media-addiction/</guid></item><item><title>美国银行表示，随着市场看到一把可能“蚕食”利润的“双刃剑”，围绕人工智能革命的疑虑正在出现</title><link>https://fortune.com/2026/02/20/doubts-ai-revolution-emerging-bank-of-america-double-edged-sword-cannibalize/</link><description>&lt;img src="https://fortune.com/img-assets/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/GettyImages-2262656352.jpg?w=1440&amp;amp;q=75" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 10:53:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://fortune.